Package: gp3bayes
Title: Contract-First Bayesian Workflows for Hierarchical Behavioural Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(
      given = "Stefanos",
      family = "Balaskas",
      email = "s.balaskas@ac.upatras.gr",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2444-9796")
    )
Description: Provides transparent, contract-first infrastructure for Bayesian
    analysis of repeated-measures and hierarchical behavioural data. It
    supports explicit model contracts, readiness audits, deterministic
    simulation for hierarchical binary outcomes, recorded data
    transformations, inspectable prior specifications, and prior predictive
    checks. The core package does not fit models and requires no Bayesian
    backend, compiler, hardware-specific export, or external dataset.
